---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy — ConsultingDemand"
  description="How ConsultingDemand collects, uses, and protects your personal data."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="legal-hero-inner">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="legal-date">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="legal-content">
    <div class="legal-inner">
      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>ConsultingDemand ("we", "us", "our") operates the website consultingdemand.com. We are committed to protecting your privacy and handling your personal data transparently.</p>

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We may collect the following types of information:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Contact information</strong> — name, email address, and company name when you subscribe to our newsletter, submit a contact form, or request a consultant match.</li>
        <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — pages visited, time on site, referral source, browser type, and device information. Collected via analytics tools.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — small text files stored on your device to improve your experience. See our <a href="/cookies">Cookie Policy</a> for details.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>We use collected information to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Deliver and improve our content and services.</li>
        <li>Send our newsletter and editorial updates (only with your consent).</li>
        <li>Match you with consultants when you submit a brief.</li>
        <li>Analyse site usage to improve performance and editorial decisions.</li>
        <li>Respond to your enquiries and provide customer support.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Legal Basis for Processing</h2>
      <p>We process personal data on the following bases:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Consent</strong> — for newsletter subscriptions and cookie usage.</li>
        <li><strong>Legitimate interest</strong> — for analytics, site improvement, and responding to enquiries.</li>
        <li><strong>Contractual necessity</strong> — for consultant matching services you request.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Sharing</h2>
      <p>We do not sell your personal data. We may share data with:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Email service providers to deliver newsletters.</li>
        <li>Analytics providers to understand site usage.</li>
        <li>Consulting partners, but only when you explicitly submit a brief requesting a match.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>We retain personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes described above, or as required by law. Newsletter subscribers can unsubscribe at any time, and we will delete their email within 30 days.</p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent at any time.</li>
        <li>Object to processing based on legitimate interest.</li>
        <li>Request data portability.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@consultingdemand.com">privacy@consultingdemand.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>8. Security</h2>
      <p>We implement appropriate technical and organisational measures to protect your data. However, no method of transmission over the Internet is 100% secure.</p>

      <h2>9. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify subscribers of material changes via email. The date at the top of this page indicates when it was last revised.</p>

      <h2>10. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related enquiries, email <a href="mailto:privacy@consultingdemand.com">privacy@consultingdemand.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.legal-hero { background: var(--black); padding: 100px 48px 80px; text-align: center; }
.legal-hero-inner { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; }
.legal-hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px); font-weight: 900; color: var(--white); letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 12px; }
.legal-date { font-family: var(--font-ui); font-size: 14px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4); }

.legal-content { padding: 64px 48px 100px; }
.legal-inner { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
.legal-inner h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: var(--gray-800); margin: 40px 0 16px; letter-spacing: -0.02em; }
.legal-inner h2:first-child { margin-top: 0; }
.legal-inner p { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 16px; }
.legal-inner ul { margin: 0 0 16px 24px; }
.legal-inner li { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 16px; color: var(--gray-600); line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 8px; }
.legal-inner a { color: var(--orange); text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; transition: color 0.2s; }
.legal-inner a:hover { color: var(--orange-dark); }

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .legal-hero { padding: 56px 20px 48px; }
  .legal-content { padding: 40px 20px 64px; }
}
</style>
